# Combined requirements for the unified WebVideo2NAS image (api + worker).
# The image switches role at startup based on the ROLE env var (see entrypoint.sh).
# Direct dependencies only — pip-compile produces requirements.txt with full
# transitive pins + SHA256 hashes for supply-chain integrity.

